org.opensaml.saml.saml1.core

Interface Response

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ResponseAbstractType, SAMLObject, SignableSAMLObject, SignableXMLObject, org.opensaml.core.xml.XMLObject

    public interface Response
extends ResponseAbstractType
    This interface defines how the object representing a SAML1 Response element behaves.
